      <title>Electrek 称特斯拉 Cyber​​truck 交付因雨刷问题推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-15/tesla-cybertruck-deliveries-delayed-over-wipers-electrek-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Electrek 报道，由于挡风玻璃雨刷出现问题，特斯拉公司已停止 Cyber​​truck 的交付。]]></description>
